00:15:22,806 --> 00:15:26,106
he was welcomed as a hero,

276
00:15:33,419 --> 00:15:35,347
You must be perplexed by how

277
00:15:35,347 --> 00:15:40,539
Napoleon, who lost the territories, 
and abandoned his army,

278
00:15:40,539 --> 00:15:42,755
is welcomed as a hero?

279
00:15:42,755 --> 00:15:49,020
This was due to the extensive pro-Napoleon 
