00:22:58,643 --> 00:23:02,168
rather they were there to liberate them 
from kings and emperors

408
00:23:02,168 --> 00:23:04,557
who had oppressed them.

409
00:23:04,557 --> 00:23:09,202
This is why in Milan, Italy 
Napoleon was viewed as a hero.

410
00:23:09,202 --> 00:23:13,480
For liberating them from Austrian rule under King Francis II.

411
00:23:13,804 --> 00:23:16,648
Italian revolutionary and poet Yugo Foscolo

