00:23:16,648 --> 00:23:19,092
in 1802, said this about him:

413
00:23:19,092 --> 00:23:21,570
"I will name you, therefore, Bonaparte,

414
00:23:21,570 --> 00:23:26,161
with the unheard-of title of Liberator 
of Peoples and Founder of Republics."

415
00:23:26,161 --> 00:23:29,599
Additionally, in 1803, on of the 
most renowned music composer,

